                <div class="example-card">
                    <div class="example-scenario">Scenario A</div>
                    <h3>The Student Housing Case</h3>
                    <p>40 students report broken heating in winter. 1 landlord disputes it.</p>
                    <div class="example-result">
                        <strong>Result:</strong> Algorithm weights the 40 verified student reports significantly higher. Issue flagged as critical. Landlord's dispute noted but doesn't override pattern.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="example-card">
                    <div class="example-scenario">Scenario B</div>
                    <h3>The Competitor Attack</h3>
                    <p>50 negative reviews appear in 24 hours, all from new accounts, similar language.</p>
                    <div class="example-result">
                        <strong>Result:</strong> Anti-brigading system flags suspicious pattern. Reviews held for additional verification. IP analysis reveals coordination. Reviews rejected.
